<div id="title"><span class="left"><i class="fa fa-hand-peace-o title"></i>Welcome to appdata backup</span></div>
<p>Welcome to the appdata backup plugin!</p>
<p>This plugin allows you to back up and restore all your appdata content! It takes care of everything (stop/start
    docker containers) including some extras (update docker containers)</p>

<div id="title"><span class="left"><i class="fa fa-cog title"></i>Settings</span></div>

<form>
    <dl>
        <dt><b>Appdata Share (Source):</b></dt>
        <dd><input type='text' class='setting' id="source" name="source"
                   data-pickfilter="HIDE_FILES_FILTER" data-pickroot="/mnt/" data-pickfolders="true"/></dd>

        <dt><b>Destination Share:</b></dt>
        <dd><input type='text' class='setting' id="destinationShare" name="shareFolder"
                   data-pickfilter="HIDE_FILES_FILTER" data-pickfolders="true"></dd>

        <dt><b>Use Compression?</b></dt>
        <dd><select class='setting' id='compression'>
                <option value='no'>No</option>
                <option value='yes'>Yes</option>
            </select>
        </dd>

        <dt><b>Verify Backups?</b><br/>This can lead to broken backups - Only enable if you know what you do!</dt>
        <dd><select class='setting' id='verify'>
                <option value='no'>No</option>
                <option value='yes'>Yes</option>
            </select>
        </dd>

        <dt><b>Ignore errors during backup?</b><br/>This can lead to broken backups - Only enable if you know what you
            do!
        </dt>
        <dd><select class='setting' id='ignoreBackupErrors'>
                <option value='no'>No</option>
                <option value='yes'>Yes</option>
            </select>
        </dd>

        <dt><b>Create separate archives (one per folder)?</b></dt>
        <dd><select class='setting' id='separateArchives'>
                <option value='no'>No</option>
                <option value='yes'>Yes</option>
            </select>
        </dd>

        <dt>&nbsp;</dt>
        <dd><input type="button" value="Save"/> <input type="reset" value="Discard"/>
            <button style="margin-left: 15px;">Manual backup</button>
        </dd>
    </dl>
</form>

